#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>You didn't import demo data?</strong> You can still do it. Go to "
"Apps &gt; Industries &gt; Upgrade your Hardware Shop package and check the "
"related box."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງແມ່ນບໍ່?</strong> ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢູ່. ໄປທີ່ ແອັບ &gt; ອຸດສາ"
"ຫະກຳ &gt; ອັບເກຣດແພັກເກດ ຮ້ານຮາດແວ ຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ ໝາຍເອົາຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"A free, personalized, integrated <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">Website</span></strong> in a few clicks. Start receiving orders "
"directly in Odoo and go live with your <strong><span style=\"color: "
"#875A7B;\">E-shop</span></strong> in a few minutes."
msgstr ""
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">ເວັບໄຊ</span></strong> ທີ່ເປັນສ່ວນຕົວ ແລະ ຄົ"
"ບວົງຈອນໄດ້ໂດຍບໍ່ເສຍຄ່າ ພາຍໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດຄລິກ. ເລີ່ມຮັບຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ໂດຍກົງໃນ Odoo ແລະ ເປີດໃຊ້ <strong>"
"<span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">ຮ້ານຄ້າອອນລາຍ</span></strong> ຂອງທ່ານພາຍໃນບໍ່ເທົ່າໃດ"
"ນາທີ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Ace Hardware is already registered in your database; select it using the "
"\"Customer\" button."
msgstr ""
"Ace Hardware ໄດ້ຖືກລົງທະບຽນໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນຂອງທ່ານແລ້ວ; ເລືອກມັນໂດຍໃຊ້ປຸ່ມ \"ລູກຄ້າ\"."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add your customer, and the product they want."
msgstr "ເພີ່ມລູກຄ້າຂອງທ່ານ, ແລະ ສິນຄ້າທີ່ພວກເຂົາຕ້ອງການ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any specific manufacture process in your shop? (Cutting wood panels, "
"assemblies...). Try the <strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">Manufacture "
"App</span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"ມີຂະບວນການຜະລິດສະເພາະໃດໜຶ່ງໃນຮ້ານຂອງທ່ານບໍ່? (ການຕັດແຜ່ນໄມ້, ການປະກອບ...). ລອງໃຊ້ "
"<strong><span style=\"color: #875A7B;\">ແອັບການຜະລິດ</span></strong>"

