#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As we now have our Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc back in stock, we can "
"deliver it to our patient customers."
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກຕອນນີ້ພວກເຮົາມີສິນຄ້າ Asian. Water Proofing Hydroloc ເຂົ້າມາໃນສາງແລ້ວ, ພວກເຮົາສາ"
"ມາດສົ່ງມອບໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າທີ່ລໍຖ້າໄດ້."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"As you do not have enough products on hand, plan the shipping for later. On "
"the payment screen, you can select the \"Ship Later\" button and enter the "
"date you expect the shipment to be made."
msgstr ""
"ເນື່ອງຈາກທ່ານມີສິນຄ້າບໍ່ພຽງພໍໃນສາງ, ໃຫ້ວາງແຜນການຈັດສົ່ງພາຍຫຼັງ. ໃນໜ້າຈໍການຊຳລະເງິນ, ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອ"
"ກປຸ່ມ \"ສົ່ງພາຍຫຼັງ\" ແລະ ປ້ອນວັນທີທີ່ທ່ານຄາດວ່າຈະຈັດສົ່ງ."

