#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Welcome your customer Ace Hardware, a B2B customer. They need 2 Aqua Double "
"Soap Dish."
msgstr ""
"ຕ້ອນຮັບ Ace Hardware ລູກຄ້າ B2B ຂອງທ່ານ. ພວກເຂົາຕ້ອງການຈານວາງສະບູຄູ່ Aqua ຈຳນວນ 2 ອັນ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:hardware_shop.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບ! ຂໍໃຫ້ມ່ວນກັບການສຳຫຼວດ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model:product.attribute.value,name:hardware_shop.product_attribute_value_4
msgid "White"
msgstr "ສີຂາວ"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຕ້ອງການປຶກສາກ່ຽວກັບການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານກັບພວກເຮົາ ຫຼື ໄປຕໍ່ໃຫ້ໄກກວ່ານີ້ບໍ່?"

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ໃນແຜງຄວບຄຸມຫຼັກ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can observe that the Purchase Order suggests a replenishment of 100 products. This is due to the existing \"Reordering rule\" on this specific product. \n"
"                    <br/><br/>\n"
"                    The reordering rule will ensure that our stock doesn't go below the minimum quantity indicated and replenishes to the maximum quantity encoded."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຈະສັງເກດເຫັນວ່າໃບສັ່ງຊື້ແນະນຳໃຫ້ເຕີມສິນຄ້າ 100 ຊຸດ. ນີ້ແມ່ນຍ້ອນ \"ກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນ\" "
"(Reordering rule) ທີ່ມີຢູ່ສຳລັບສິນຄ້ານີ້.\n"
"                    <br/><br/>\n"
"                    ກົດເກນການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນຈະຊ່ວຍຮັບປະກັນວ່າສິນຄ້າໃນສາງຂອງພວກເຮົາຈະບໍ່ຫຼຸດລົງຕໍ່າກວ່າປ"
"ະລິມານຂັ້ນຕໍ່າທີ່ກຳນົດໄວ້ ແລະ ຈະເຕີມສິນຄ້າໃຫ້ຮອດປະລິມານສູງສຸດທີ່ລະບຸ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can see that Ace Hardware benefits from a specific pricelist rebate of "
"5% on everything they buy. Manage pricelists by navigating to Products &gt; "
"Pricelists."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຈະເຫັນວ່າ Ace Hardware ໄດ້ຮັບສ່ວນຫຼຸດ 5% ຈາກລາຍການລາຄາສະເພາະສຳລັບທຸກຢ່າງທີ່ພວກເຂົາຊື້. ຈັດ"
"ການລາຍການລາຄາໂດຍໄປທີ່ ສິນຄ້າ &gt; ລາຍການລາຄາ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ສຳເລັດກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງນີ້ແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີໃນການປັບແຕ່ງການຕັ້ງຄ່າ Odoo ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອ"
"ງການຂອງທຸລະກິດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just need to send the Request For Quotation by email, or to confirm it "
"manually once the order is placed."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານພຽງແຕ່ຕ້ອງສົ່ງໃບຮ້ອງຂໍລາຄາ (RFQ) ຜ່ານອີເມລ, ຫຼື ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງເມື່ອມີການວາງຄຳສັ່ງຊື້ແລ້ວ."

#. module: hardware_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hardware_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly implement with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ເພື່ອເບິ່ງພາບລວມຂອງຂະບວນການຕ່າງໆ ທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດນຳໃຊ້ໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງ"
"ໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກດ Odoo ນີ້."

